%!PS-Adobe-3.0 EPSF-3.0
%%BoundingBox: 20 118 575 673
%%Creator: FreeHEP Graphics2D Driver
%%Producer: com.maplesoft.mathdoc.view.plot.paint.PlotPSGraphics2D Revision: 12753 
%%For: 
